      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Gmail Reply Agent\n\n**Steps:**\n\n1. Check email for unreplied messages \n2. Get the messages\n3. Add the message to corresponding labels: \"enquiries\", \"consultation\", \"complains\"\n4. Draft a reply for the email\n",
