        "gmailOAuth2": {
          "id": "R9uZAlBUPByGXVuD",
          "name": "Gmail OAuth2 API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an Email Reply assistant and you have to reply to a user's email:\n\n\"\"\"\nSubject: {{ $json.Subject }}\n\nBody: {{ $json.snippet }}\n\"\"\"\n\nFollowing the following reply rules:\n- You should maintain a friendly tune while replying\n- Ensure the content is humanized and all em-dashes are removed\nStructure Output:\n- Ensure the output are in json format below is a sample:\n{\n  \"subject\": \"string\",\n  \"body\": \"Hello, Abdulkareem. We got your message\",\n  \"label\":\"enquiries\",\n  \"label_id\": \"Label_3345\"\n}\n- The body should be html friendly.\n\nYou have access to the following tools:\ngmail_get_labels - This provides you with the required labels and use only the user created labes (\"enquiries\", \"consultation\", \"complains\")\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        -144,
        -16
      ],
      "id": "1510bf4f-6e58-4afb-821d-7ae0289508bb",
      "name": "AI Agent",
      "executeOnce": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsonSchemaExample": "{\n  \"subject\": \"string\",\n  \"body\": \"Hello, Abdulkareem. We got your message\",\n  \"label\":\"enquiries\",\n  \"label_id\": \"Label_3345\"\n}\n"
      },
